<normalizedToken id="F999F4DBF6CFCF88F654A84DC11141BF" originalValue="Kalaminthenblättriger" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">Kalaminthenblaettriger</normalizedToken>
Ehrenpreis
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="8BBC3707DE3E1B1D29DB24D230181D18" pageId="null" pageNumber="198" type="description">
<paragraph id="EB0E1C5FCF0C7F81D7FC2189AC7EE956" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">
5-20 cm hoch. 
<emphasis id="C36401B5B8724F0E383E75A94ED560B6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">
Alle 
<normalizedToken id="1EA76AC05FA0091DB36D9DDE40D96958" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
ungeteilt
</emphasis>
, meist 
<normalizedToken id="16895BE616E36501E4B1FFBF08456C7E" originalValue="gezähnt" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">gezaehnt</normalizedToken>
, die untern 0,5-1 cm lang und 0,3-0,6 cm breit. 
<emphasis id="13C2EF2722E3AEFE1F661481A330367C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">Kelchzipfel zur Fruchtzeit 2</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="AF0A7601B73DE0D16675C8F978DC723F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">3 mm lang. Krone im Durchmesser 3</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="E33B1478A0EBA3DAD13C5F1FE3089B79" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">5 mm</emphasis>
, hellblau, dunkler geadert. 
<emphasis id="0338639F4A3676FA115BA3A1BD1FD2BD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">
<pageBreakToken id="D1915441C12C86B42BD95843F7E55728" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">Frucht</pageBreakToken>
deutlich breiter als lang
</emphasis>
, 4-5 mm breit und 
<emphasis id="2B0C3C91CED662317F844A05A975895B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">2</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="F076B605FAA59C19E17FA86872A943E8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">3 mm lang.</emphasis>
Griffel 1-1,5 mm lang. 
<emphasis id="3F64B2B58AD19282F05AD9355C510579" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">
Samen 
<normalizedToken id="94E2FBEC2FA50D59BD3532A87FC3E145" originalValue="schildförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">schildfoermig</normalizedToken>
, glatt, 0,6
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="281E1DC00CF21EF591B7BBE6E7AD6AA6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">
0,8 mm lang, meist 
<normalizedToken id="A68E9DDC4221B6D4E8EC52131736D8E6" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">ueber</normalizedToken>
20 Samen je Frucht.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="7E353DE0E6A1A2ACA845567E8ED6708B" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="0DEAF3ECADA44E3B455858AB7770D7BF" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="66D2364B09756E95CC11053D55925B9E" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">
<emphasis id="C5803148B3CAE9DCA87A00FF47F55481" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="8C4880ABF5E2B891AE4E3D8EDD92C797" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">14:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischem Garten (Hofelich 1935, Afanasiyeva und Meshkova 1961). 
<emphasis id="53D4106BE85831F517E6C36E00E51C58" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="9A0ADA7627F2312A1D55E37BCF423CAF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">16:</emphasis>
Material aus 
<normalizedToken id="B2B251C929DFC50553B0400E744CBEE3" originalValue="Rumänien" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">Rumaenien</normalizedToken>
(Tarnavschi 1948).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E0976D1D6F1BA8C63BCE24444AE8C89A" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">
<emphasis id="E8F06DD953FC982347172E35964E3279" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan. Feuchte, 
<normalizedToken id="0657B22F1E20AD612015671D1F0F144B" originalValue="nährstoffreiche" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">naehrstoffreiche</normalizedToken>
, kalkarme, lehmige 
<normalizedToken id="DBA61B7C38285C5C33E682AAE12249A8" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. Feuchte 
<normalizedToken id="EA6AD453401249CB50D0250DC159AF7D" originalValue="Äcker" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">Aecker</normalizedToken>
, Ackerrinnen. 
<emphasis id="1BD98BD3AA183210AD7DBD71F1E2D303" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">Centunculo-Anthoceretum</emphasis>
Moor 1936.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1E6E8E2D3F574F6AD3B7B8F246918AF9" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">
<emphasis id="B59B7C74ACB73358B89A90483B327C2C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="9C3AC826ABCED37EC39878ABD71DDAA9" originalValue="Südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">Suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="459F81020CB49E6AA4D04EBAEABAD123" originalValue="Nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">Nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="9C8976150D07C8EEA282A85E5CC3D867" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
vereinzelt bis Nordfrankreich, Oberrheinische Tiefebene, Alpen, Donaubecken, Krim, Kaukasus, Kleinasien (?). - Im Gebiet nur im 
<normalizedToken id="DA3E2527F59DA90A74B2D8E65E6DF0E0" originalValue="nördlichen" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">noerdlichen</normalizedToken>
, westlichen und 
<normalizedToken id="B39D75CFED8ADF8FDD3118F166BB2096" originalValue="südlichen" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">suedlichen</normalizedToken>
Teil, selten und 
<normalizedToken id="64F4C7FA4E9645F3E9B6F1D7C6B0D023" originalValue="unbeständig" pageId="null" pageNumber="198">unbestaendig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
